# Save and Recovery Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Editor
    participant DocumentManager
    participant AtomicWriter
    participant RecoveryStore
    participant Disk

    User->>Editor: Type text
    Editor->>DocumentManager: Mark buffer dirty
    DocumentManager->>RecoveryStore: Debounced recovery snapshot

    User->>Editor: Cmd+S
    Editor->>DocumentManager: Save active buffer
    DocumentManager->>Disk: Check exists + metadata/hash

    alt File changed externally
        DocumentManager->>User: Show conflict options
    else Safe to save
        DocumentManager->>AtomicWriter: Write temp file
        AtomicWriter->>Disk: Atomic replace original
        Disk-->>AtomicWriter: Success
        AtomicWriter-->>DocumentManager: Save confirmed
        DocumentManager->>RecoveryStore: Delete recovery buffer
        DocumentManager->>Editor: Mark clean
    end
```
